      "content": "You should absolutely not mix melatonin and Zolpidem without consulting your doctor, as combining them can lead to dangerous side effects. Since you need sleep, you should definitely follow the dosage instructions your doctor gave you for the Zolpidem, and maybe try adding a magnesium supplement, which is a natural sleep aid. If you're still struggling, go ahead and ask your doctor for a different, more effective solution.",
